@startuml 2WAY_Design
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

rectangle "Trusted Party A" as PartyA
rectangle "Trusted Party B" as PartyB
rectangle "Trusted Party C" as PartyC

rectangle "2WAY_Design Core" as Core {
  rectangle "Trust Network Manager" as TrustManager
  rectangle "Data Exchange Engine" as ExchangeEngine
  rectangle "Auth/Authz Service" as AuthService
}

database "Private Data Store" as DataStore

PartyA --> Core : Secure Connection
PartyB --> Core : Secure Connection
PartyC --> Core : Secure Connection

TrustManager --> ExchangeEngine : Manages Trust
ExchangeEngine --> AuthService : Validates Access
ExchangeEngine --> DataStore : Stores/Retrieves Data

note right of Core
  Implements:
  - Trust Network Pattern
  - Secure Data Exchange
  - Authentication/Authorization
end note
@enduml